title: It Kills
lyrics:
Stay beside the storm that linger in the clouds
Starve inside of me, there's no way out
Like I for anything that burns me down
The more and more I try
I crave

I need

It kills

I can't break my heart



I cry so long

It kills

I can't break my heart



Live within the walls that filter out the sound

I take the best of me, then turn around

I aim for enemy that tears me down

The more and more I try



I crave

I need

It kills

I can't break my heart



I cry so long

It kills

I can't break my heart
